'''Henri-Yozefu Koumba Bididi'''  yavutse 15 Nyakanga 1957), ni umunya Gabo ukora filimi, akandika filimi ndetse anakora kuri  Tv nka  televiziyo manager umusaruro ahanini utaziguye muma documentary films<ref>http://africultures.com/personnes?no=3204</ref>.  Yakoze documentaire nyinshi zamamaye cyane harimo ''na Necklace ya King'' na ''Le Singe Fou''<ref>https://cines.com/en/directors/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi</ref> . Usibye icyerekezo, yanakoze, yandika cyangwa ayobora inyandiko nyinshi kuri tereviziyo<ref>http://www.africine.org/personne/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi/3204</ref>.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 15 Nyakanga 1957 i Omboué, muri [[Gabon]] . Yarangije amashuri ya firime muri École supérieure d'études cinématographiques (ESEC) mu Bufaransa<ref>https://www.allocine.fr/personne/fichepersonne_gen_cpersonne=69396.html</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1983, Bididi yakoraga nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe gukina filime ''Équatur'' iyobowe na Serge Gainsbourg <ref>https://ifcinema.institutfrancais.com/en/search?q_text=Henri-Joseph%20Koumba%20Bididi</ref>. Hanyuma mu 1986, yasinyiye muri firime ngufi ''Le singe fou'' <ref>https://en.unifrance.org/directories/person/306060/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi</ref>. Yahawe igihembo kubera kunenga abanyamakuru b'Abarabu mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Carthage ndetse anahabwa igihembo gikomeye cya Filime ngufi mu iserukiramuco rya Filime na Televiziyo rya 10 rya Panafrican rya Ouagadougou (FESPACO) mu 1987<ref>https://cines.com/en/movie-script/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi</ref>. 

Kuva mu 1988 kugeza 1991, Bididi yari umuyobozi w'ishami rya radiyo na televiziyo byo mu karere ka ' Haut-Ogoué <ref>https://www.eyrolles.com/Litterature/Livre/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi-le-dernier-nabab-du-cinema-gabonais-9782414237135/</ref>'. Kuva mu 1991 kugeza 1994, Bididi yazamuwe kuba umuyobozi wungirije mushya wa Radio Télévision Gabonaise (RTG)<ref>https://www.eyrolles.com/Litterature/Livre/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi-le-dernier-nabab-du-cinema-gabonais-9782414237135/</ref>. Mu 2000, yakomeje gukora nk'umuyobozi wa tereviziyo akaba na producer wa filime ye ya mbere yakinnye, ''Les Couilles de l'éléphant'' <ref>https://www.librairie-gallimard.com/livre/9782414237135-henri-joseph-koumba-bididi-le-dernier-nabab-du-cinema-gabonais-kevin-biyoghe-serge/</ref>. Iyi filime yerekanwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya 17 rya [[Afurika]] ryabereye i [[Wagadugu|Ouagadougou]], [[Burukina Faso|Burkina]] Faso. Mu 1994, Bididi yayoboye ibice bibiri bya serivise ya ''L'auberge du Salut''<ref>https://www.alamy.com/djogo-year-2002-gabon-france-director-henri-joseph-koumba-bididi-image225298644.html</ref> . 

Muri uwo mwaka, yayoboye filime yerekana ''Le collier du Makoko'', iyi ikaba ari filime ihenze cyane muri [[Afurika]] yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara yarashwe hamwe na miliyoni 4 z'amayero<ref>https://www.binged.com/person/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi/</ref>. Filime yateguwe mu myaka 4, aho gufata amashusho byatwaye amezi atatu<ref>https://afrocinestream.com/R%C3%A9alisateur/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi-gabon/</ref>. Iyi filime yakiriwe neza mu maserukiramuco mpuzamahanga ya filime kandi yegukana igihembo cy’abacamanza kidasanzwe ndetse n’igihembo cyo gusobanura abagabo mu iserukiramuco rya Khouribga 2012 ryabereye muri [[Maroke|Maroc]]<ref>https://mubi.com/cast/henri-joseph-koumba-bididi</ref>. Yatsindiye kandi igihembo cyo Gusobanura mu iserukiramuco rya Ecrans Noirs 2012 ryabereye muri Kameruni nk'icyo gihembo cy’amajwi meza na posita nziza muri FESPACO 2013. Muri 2013<ref>https://www.cinemaafrica.uni-bayreuth.de/de/unsere-gaeste/filmemacher-im-gespraech/Henri-Joseph-Koumba-Bididi/index.html</ref>, iyi filime yatsindiye igihembo cy'abari bitabiriye iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Masuku 2013 ryabereye i Gabon.<ref>http://www.clapnoir.org/spip.php?mot281</ref> 

